      • doubleHash

        private int doubleHash(K key,
                       int num)
        private method takes two parametr. Uses double hashing formula((hash1Code(key)+num*hash2Code(key))%data.length) calculate the new index for double hashing because first index is either not empty or there is removed element
        Parameters:
        key - is unique id for map values
        num - this parametr uses in double hashing formula if index is not appopriarite num increases
        Returns:
        returns new index for unique key
